                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="VariableName">1 ×</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">. It is kinematically-defined - typically the </text><text styleclass="Element">Base-Part</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="VariableName">2 ×</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">&#32;</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-transform:uppercase; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">Parts</text><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-5.gif" scale="100.00%" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:italic; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:italic; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">.</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;"> They are </text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#ff0000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">not</text><text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;"> kinematically-defined.</text></para>
                <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">&#32;</text><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Body Text" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text"> : a</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Interface">Free-Part</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">. It is joined to the </text><text styleclass="Element">Base-Part</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> with a </text><text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Element">Part</text>&#32;<image src="Red-14-5.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption"> :</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Part-Free" styleclass="Element">Completely Free Part</link><text styleclass="Body Text"> . It does not have joints, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">before</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> you do </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Ball-Joint</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></li>
                </list>
