                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal;">If you cannot select the two(2) </text><text styleclass="Element">Points</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> to add a </text><text styleclass="Element">Ball-Joint</text>, disable<text styleclass="Bullets"> the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Edit-AutoUpdate" styleclass="Bullets">Auto-Update tool</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text>and try again.</para>
